    <item>
      <title>台湾官员称中国军队最近实行克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/china-military-exercising-restraint-lately-taiwan-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾安全官员表示，中国似乎正在减弱对台湾的军事压力，并警告北京仍可能继续其外交孤立行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/china-military-exercising-restraint-lately-taiwan-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 06:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
